  <div class="functionIntro">
   <p class="code">
    <span class="IF"><span class="specialcharacters">GenericLinearCombinationOperator<span class="openbracket">[</span>&lt;<span class="verticalbar">|</span><span class="verticalbar">|</span>&gt;<span class="closebracket">]</span><span class="openbracket">[</span>MonList<span class="closebracket">]</span></span></span>
   </p>
   <p class="code-description">returns a generic linear combination with the elements of MonList and its coefficients. The coefficients are given by <span class="special-character formalcharacter FormalA">a</span>$i, with i from 1 to Length[MonList].
</p>
  </div>
  <div class="functionIntro">
   <p class="code">
    <span class="IF">GenericLinearCombinationOperator<span class="openbracket">[</span><span class="specialcharacters">&lt;<span class="verticalbar">|</span></span>&quot;unique&quot;<span class="special-character Rule">&#62754;</span>True<span class="specialcharacters"><span class="verticalbar">|</span>&gt;</span><span class="closebracket">]</span><span class="openbracket">[</span>MonList<span class="closebracket">]</span></span>
   </p>
   <p class="code-description">The index for the coefficients are given in a unique way.
</p>
  </div>
  <div class="functionIntro">
   <p class="code">
    <span class="IF">GenericLinearCombinationOperator<span class="openbracket">[</span><span class="specialcharacters">&lt;<span class="verticalbar">|</span></span>&quot;coeff&quot;<span class="special-character Rule">&#62754;</span> coeff_name<span class="specialcharacters"><span class="verticalbar">|</span>&gt;</span><span class="closebracket">]</span><span class="openbracket">[</span>MonList<span class="closebracket">]</span></span>
   </p>
   <p class="code-description">The coefficients are coeff_name$i. </p>
